Pak has four loop types:

```pak
-- infinite loop
loop {
    if done { break }
}

-- while loop
while condition {
    -- body
}

-- do-while
do {
    -- runs at least once
} while condition

-- for range
for i in 0..10 {
    -- i goes 0..9
}
```

For loops iterate over ranges. The end is exclusive.

```pak
for i in 0..10 {
    -- i = 0, 1, 2, ..., 9
}

-- with index and element
for i, x in collection {
